A German man was sentenced to five and a half years in prison on Tuesday for paying to watch children being abused via webcam. Prosecutors said livestream sex abuse cases are becoming increasingly prevalent while the Philippines has called on other countries to impose tougher sentences on such offenders. Read more: The Philippines' booming cybersex industry Send  Facebook   Twitter   Google+   Whatsapp   
